name: Hold
description: The "Hold" AR project illustrates the physical action, holding a "global" fist, which symbolizes strength. This force has many concepts, from aggressive intervention in geopolitic, to the pressure of a rapidly evolving  future with environmental changes. Anthropomorphic figure - the image of humanity, its sculptural contours create the effect of tension, which opposes its force, which seeks freedom through struggle. By Vlas Belov Website: http://vlasbelov.tilda.ws/
